'''巨駝屬'''（{{lang-xm|Megacamelus}}）為已滅絕的[[駱駝|駱駝]]，棲息於10.3—4.9[[百萬年前|百萬年前]]，[[中新世|中新世]]至[[上新世|上新世]]的[[北美洲|北美洲]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://paleodb.org/cgi-bin/bridge.pl?action=checkTaxonInfo&taxon_no=42531&is_real_user=1 |title=PaleoBiology Database: ''Megacamelus'', basic info |access-date=2020-12-13 |archive-date=2012-10-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121013225328/http://paleodb.org/cgi-bin/bridge.pl?action=checkTaxonInfo&taxon_no=42531&is_real_user=1 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

巨駝為體型最大的駱駝之一，其他巨型駱駝則包括''{{link-en|Megatylopus}}''、[[大駝|大駝]]與{{link-en|巨副駝屬|Paracamelus|巨副駝}}<ref>{{Cite journal | last1 = Zazula | first1 = G. D. | last2 = Macphee | first2 = R. D. | last3 = Hall | first3 = E. | last4 = Hewitson | first4 = S. | title = Osteological Assessment of Pleistocene Camelops hesternus (Camelidae: Camelinae: Camelini) from Alaska and Yukon | year = 2016 | journal = American Museum Novitates | volume = 2016 | issue = 3866 | pages = 1–46 | url = https://digitallibrary.amnh.org/bitstream/handle/2246/6677/N3866.pdf | access-date = 22 September 2019 | doi = 10.1206/3866.1 | ref = harv | archive-date = 2019-09-22 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190922113528/https://digitallibrary.amnh.org/bitstream/handle/2246/6677/N3866.pdf | dead-url = no }}<!-- {{Harvnb|Zazula|Macphee|Hall|Hewitson|2016|loc=E.g. p. 16}} --></ref>。

==分類學==
巨駝屬的學名「''Megacamelus''」最早由弗里克於1929年命名，並由弗里克與哈尼分類至駱駝科之下<ref>J. G. Honey, J. A. Harrison, D. R. Prothero and M. S. Stevens. 1998. Camelidae. In C. M. Janis, K. M. Scott, and L. L. Jacobs (eds.), Evolution of Tertiary Mammals of North America 1:439-462</ref>。

==化石出土地點==
巨駝的化石發現於[[內布拉斯加州|內布拉斯加州]]、[[愛達荷州|愛達荷州]]及[[南加利福尼亞州|南加利福尼亞州]]。

